title: Nutra Sonic 1020 Professional 4 Speed Face and Body Cleansing System, Lavender
description: Nutra sonic skin cleansing is gentle, yet effective enough to helps to reduce, eliminate and prevent ingrown hair or razor burn. 4 speeds: low frequency for sensitive skin, high frequency for normal skin, body brush speed for overall cleansing and jitter mode pulsating oscillation for microdermabrasion. daily use will help improve skin texture for a younger looking skin. fully waterproof and rechargeable, use it without risk in the shower, tub or at the sink. gentle enough to be use twice a day.
